description:
Agata is normally protective of his younger sister, but his genius IQ goes out the window when he becomes convinced that Saaya and Tsubaki are in love with each other!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: He`s Interested in the Sister and the Brother`s Interested in Him
Imouto no Ki ni Naru Aitsu ga Ki ni Naru Ani
妹の気になるアイツが気になる兄
